慮不開發，還有300多平方公里可用。但爭議多年，開發仍遙遙無期。<br />\n<br />\n但最尾兩段都係廢話"},{"pid":"f8b54ce62bcc2e55835912175d62f7ac917cb5dd","tid":1551754,"uid":119793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"文中所講嘅情況其實中國自己都過之而無不及<br />\n只不過目前佢地嘅強權迫壓下啲人唔敢爆<br />\n而香港爆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edea738e6469275de1b9ceda6f09bed268a8118","tid":1551754,"uid":31151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:16:58.000Z","msg":"最後又係諗d屎橋出黎 例如大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e984940093919b799ed9c0e2631e5d07635f52e2","tid":1551754,"uid":56023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a5d85bf4ff1bb0610fa818e513be5b6acba833e5","tid":1551754,"uid":272186,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:13:19.000Z","msg":"又扮懷柔 然後一鋪陰9你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"Exac7ly"},{"pid":"6dad7b21efbe9feb0e718a6168e55480f959fa32","tid":1551754,"uid":145277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8edea738e6469275de1b9ceda6f09bed268a8118","tid":1551754,"uid":31151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:16:58.000Z","msg":"最後又係諗d屎橋出黎 例如大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"錠我地去大灣區咪解決左土地問題lol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，土共思維係咁"},{"pid":"87baf295f4a75bd940e08bf7be079255fd2f5428","tid":1551754,"uid":203889,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"22892a1c274aca907373fa6ffc471b1b1747982d","tid":1551754,"uid":149978,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"大陸第一次支持香港撇取「小政府、大市場」<br />\n<br />\n似乎真係開始「時代革命」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"屌佢地不嬲都大政府架啦<br />\n你睇馬雲辛辛苦苦搞左個阿里巴巴，最後都要讓俾國家管<br />\n<br />\n真係乜都俾晒政府管，香港一撚定死得更加快"},{"pid":"a5e6096c0eed0e7da63ebd3215a0ac55d0